entry.value: select cast(recvtime as timestamp) + (interval '2 hour') as FechaHora, entityid as Dispositivo, attrname as Atributo, cast(attrvalue as float) as Valor from openiot.x002f where attrtype = 'string' and entityid like '%Calidad%' and attrname not in ('n','d')

select cast(recvtime as timestamp) + (interval '2 hour') as FechaHora, entityid as Dispositivo, attrname as Atributo, cast(attrvalue as float) as Valor from openiot.x002f where attrtype = 'string' and entityid like '%Calidad%' and attrname not in ('n','d')

select date_trunc('minute', fechahora + (interval '2 hour')) as fechahora, dispositivo, atributo, avg(valor) as valor from openiot.th_sensores where age(now(),fechahora) <= '00:01:00.000000' group by date_trunc('minute', fechahora + (interval '2 hour')), dispositivo, atributo
